{
  "texts": [
    "As explainable AI (XAI) has emerged, it can promote greater trust, transparency, and usability among users.",
    "It can become a valuable technology that can potentially improve user experience on social media.",
    "Our empirical findings show the explanation attributes (shown in thematic summary in Fig. 1) that end users require from an explainable AI system.",
    "As our findings suggest, if the explanations are provided in the correct format, the recommendation system will positively impact transparency, usability, and trust, ultimately providing a better user experience.",
    "However, the optimal explanation format for social media recommendations still needs to be discovered."
  ]
}